            </h3>
            <div id="content-plane" class="accordion-content" role="region" aria-labelledby="btn-plane" hidden>

              <p>The nearest airport to Geneva is <a href="https://www.gva.ch/fr/">Gen√®ve Cointrin</a>. Geneva
                Airport (GVA) is an international hub, the home of EasyJet and SWISS, with numerous affordable
                connections
