              <p>From Geneva Cornavin, the city center is easily accessible by public transport or on foot.
                Trams and buses from <a href="https://www.tpg.ch/fr">TPG</a> run frequently throughout the city.</p>
              <p>Geneva Airport is located just minutes from the city center, making arrival smooth and
